{"title":"江南曲","authors":["严阵"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严阵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南三月夜短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁肯舍得早眠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂起锄，放下镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小巷里细语呢喃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过石桥，穿过柳烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃枝动处灯光闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民校敞开了大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接公社的社员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村外江潮在响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头读书声喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗颗心儿钻进了书卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像犁儿把泥土深翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了读完新的一课，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不嫌三月夜短？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不觉得门前桃花开了一树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月也悄悄西偏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦秀歌枝头的毛桃脱去了花蒂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上的荷叶大似铜钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦秀季节来到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声笑语满田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们背着喷雾器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙们挑着水担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红衣紫裙青布衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮动在麦浪中间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把肥料追进根须，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把药粉撒上叶尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠儿滴在露珠儿间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日刚升起一半。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国土肥气候暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗儿长的真欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回头再看洒汗的田里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧玉般的穗子已经抽满。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}